Label: Jota Samper
Description: Jota Samper is assistant professor at the ENVD Program. He obtained his Bachelor of Arts in architecture in UNal in Medellin, a master's in city planning from MIT and a PhD on urban and regional planning, also from MIT-DUSP, where he was a lecturer for the past two years. In 2010, his project with estudio teddy cruz, exhibited at the MoMA.
